Achievements.Name: Trick in
Achievements.Description: Perform and land a trick before sliding on a rail.

Achievements.Name: Grabbing hands
Achievements.Description: Perform 3 grabs while sliding on a rail.

Achievements.Name: Magnetic rails
Achievements.Description: Slide on 4 rails within one race.

Achievements.Name: Versatile victory
Achievements.Description: Land each possible trick within one race and win.

Achievements.Name: Every trick in the book
Achievements.Description: Successfully perform each possible trick in the game.

Achievements.Name: No time to rest
Achievements.Description: After a crash, get back on track in less than 2 seconds.

Achievements.Name: Accident-free
Achievements.Description: Win a bobsled race without collisions.

Achievements.Name: Focused
Achievements.Description: Perfectly stay on the racing line in 4 bends in a bobsled race.

Achievements.Name: Catch up
Achievements.Description: Win a short track race without being in the lead in any but the last lap.

Achievements.Name: Shadow
Achievements.Description: Completely fill the slipstream bar 4 times within one short track race.

Achievements.Name: Shooting star
Achievements.Description: Biathlon: enter the shooting range in 4th place, hit all targets, leave the shooting range as 1st.

Achievements.Name: Picky
Achievements.Description: Biathlon: hit only targets 1, 3 and 5 in lap 1, only targets 2 and 4 in lap 2 and win the race.

Achievements.Name: Gateway
Achievements.Description: Cut 5 gates in a row in a downhill skiing race.

Achievements.Name: Adrenaline rush
Achievements.Description: Use adrenaline for 4 consecutive seconds in a downhill skiing race.

Achievements.Name: Crash-landing
Achievements.Description: Ski Flying: jump a distance of 220 m and crash.

Achievements.Name: Immaculate inruns
Achievements.Description: Ski Flying: don't touch the sides of the track during the inrun on both attempts.

Achievements.Name: Finished symphony
Achievements.Description: Figure skating: sustain all notes within one event with perfect or super rating.

Achievements.Name: No trouble without double
Achievements.Description: Figure skating: win an event without activating double mode.

Achievements.Name: Show-off
Achievements.Description: Snowmobile: win a race crossing the finish line in reverse.

Achievements.Name: Traction control deactivated
Achievements.Description: Snowmobile: accumulate a drifting time of 10 seconds within one race.

Achievements.Name: Last man standing
Achievements.Description: Curling: win an end without any of the opponent's stones in the house.

Achievements.Name: Clean sweep
Achievements.Description: Curling: deliver a stone with low power and place it on the button by sweeping.

Achievements.Name: Come around
Achievements.Description: Curling: curl a shot directly behind another stone in the house.

Achievements.Name: Double takeout
Achievements.Description: Curling: takeout 2 of the opponent's stones with one shot.

Achievements.Name: Air ace
Achievements.Description: Paraskiing: accumulate an airtime of 90 seconds total within one race.

Achievements.Name: Long distance flight
Achievements.Description: Paraskiing: cover a distance of 500 consecutive meters while airborne.

Achievements.Name: Botanophile
Achievements.Description: Paraskiing: finish a race without touching any bushes or trees.

Achievements.Name: Gone with the wind
Achievements.Description: Paraskiing: fly through 6 gusts of wind in a row.

Achievements.Name: Experienced
Achievements.Description: Accumulate 25 experience points within one event.

Achievements.Name: Rivalry
Achievements.Description: Tackle your rival 5 times within one race.

Achievements.Name: Beat yourself
Achievements.Description: Beat a ghost you have recorded in time trial.

Achievements.Name: Yin
Achievements.Description: Earn three golden fairplay stripes.

Achievements.Name: Yang
Achievements.Description: Earn three black fairplay stripes.

Achievements.Name: Snowflake Cup
Achievements.Description: Place among the top 3 in the Snowflake Cup.

Achievements.Name: Lady Crystal Cup
Achievements.Description: Win the Lady Crystal Cup.

Achievements.Name: Skillers United Championship
Achievements.Description: Win the Skillers United Championship.

Achievements.Name: Winter Stars World Tour Finals
Achievements.Description: Win the Winter Stars World Tour Finals.

Achievements.Name: Teambuilding
Achievements.Description: Win 3 Cups in the first chapter of the career.

Achievements.Name: All the way to the top
Achievements.Description: Win 3 Cups in the second chapter of the career.

Achievements.Name: Defending the crown
Achievements.Description: Win 3 Cups in the third chapter of the career.

Achievements.Name: Prime discipline
Achievements.Description: Max out your talent and buy all upgrades for any discipline.

Achievements.Name: Level 5
Achievements.Description: Reach level 5 in the career.

Achievements.Name: Level 10
Achievements.Description: Reach level 10 in the career.

Achievements.Name: Level 15
Achievements.Description: Reach level 15 in the career.

Achievements.Name: Warm up
Achievements.Description: Complete 5 challenges.

Achievements.Name: Amateur challenger
Achievements.Description: Complete 10 challenges.

Achievements.Name: Competent challenger
Achievements.Description: Complete 20 challenges.

Achievements.Name: Professional challenger
Achievements.Description: Complete 30 challenges.

Achievements.Name: Challenge champion
Achievements.Description: Complete all challenges.
